00:18:11.750 --> 00:18:13.580
But if you cook it,
the flavor goes away.

00:18:13.580 --> 00:18:16.640
If you chop it up too
much, it tastes like grass.

00:18:16.640 --> 00:18:19.014
And so you don't want
to chop it up too much,

00:18:19.014 --> 00:18:20.930
but you want to chop it
up enough so that when

00:18:20.930 --> 00:18:23.600
