00:18:32.390 --> 00:18:35.750
So for me, parsley
is just this like,

00:18:35.750 --> 00:18:39.037
when you say something green, I
think of the flavor of parsley.

00:18:39.037 --> 00:18:41.120
Actually one of the
restaurants I used to work at,

00:18:41.120 --> 00:18:44.990
