00:18:44.990 --> 00:18:46.840
And it was just like,
we'd make it and then

00:18:46.840 --> 00:18:49.739
incorporate it into all
these green purees that

00:18:49.739 --> 00:18:50.780
would just turn it green.

00:18:50.780 --> 00:18:52.730
And it was just
basically enhancing

00:18:52.730 --> 00:18:54.530
that green flavor,
that green color,

00:18:54.530 --> 00:18:56.280
and it just worked really well.

00:18:56.280 --> 00:18:59.010
So this helps the freshness
