trying to focus

00:34:51.409 --> 00:34:53.630
on making vegetables as
craveable and desirable

00:34:53.630 --> 00:34:54.277
as possible.

00:34:54.277 --> 00:34:56.360
And just to highlight some
of the things you said,

00:34:56.360 --> 00:34:58.735
you've got beautiful colors,
because we eat with our eyes

00:34:58.735 --> 00:34:59.510
first.

00:34:59.510 --> 00:35:01.602
You've got amazing
contrast in texture.

00:35:01.602 --> 00:35:02.435
Obviously the aroma.

00:35:02.435 --> 00:35:04.220
Can you smell this in the back?

00:35:04.220 --> 00:35:06.110
You're going to
taste it a minute.

00:35:06.110 --> 00:35:07.730
The aroma, the
textures, the color,

00:35:07.730 --> 00:35:09.590
all these different
attributes are just

00:35:09.590 --> 00:35:12.170
amazing to be able to have
something, as you put it,

00:35:12.170 --> 00:35:14.150
so desirable and
highlight the vegetable.

00:35:14.150 --> 00:35:15.330
And for people that
