job other than cooking.

00:40:08.776 --> 00:40:12.220
In some form or another, cooking
or in a restaurant, that's all

00:40:12.220 --> 00:40:13.220
I've ever done.

00:40:13.220 --> 00:40:15.430
So that's the only thing
that I know how to do.

00:40:15.430 --> 00:40:18.490
