00:40:30.610 --> 00:40:34.540
And we wanted you to come
in and feel the warmth,

00:40:34.540 --> 00:40:39.700
and be able to communicate, be
able to interact, be able to--

00:40:39.700 --> 00:40:43.900
we work the pass or work in the
kitchen, but we deliver food,

00:40:43.900 --> 00:40:46.090
and we talked to guests,
and the kitchen's open.

00:40:46.090 --> 00:40:49.540
And it's extension of our
home because the people

00:40:49.540 --> 00:40:52.510
we work with, we spend
a lot of time with.

00:40:52.510 --> 00:40:55.180
We have great relationships
with our whole team.

00:40:55.180 --> 00:40:58.550
And this is literally
part of our life.

00:40:58.550 --> 00:41:01.150
So we wanted that
feeling when you come in.

00:41:01.150 --> 00:41:04.820
And I think, it wasn't so much
