00:41:27.460 --> 00:41:30.237
And the why behind what they
do I think is so important.

00:41:30.237 --> 00:41:32.320
So thank you for sharing
that, it's very personal.

00:41:32.320 --> 00:41:34.487
We had a question in the
back and then in the front.

00:41:34.487 --> 00:41:35.111
AUDIENCE: Yeah.

00:41:35.111 --> 00:41:36.730
You talked about
going into the market

00:41:36.730 --> 00:41:38.290
