I think about dessert
in the exact same terms.

00:43:56.040 --> 00:43:58.080
I think about texture,
I think about acidity,

00:43:58.080 --> 00:44:00.660
I think about saltiness.

00:44:00.660 --> 00:44:04.020
All of those things
go into what make--

00:44:04.020 --> 00:44:06.510
whether it be savory
or sweet, balanced,

00:44:06.510 --> 00:44:09.277
and whole, and delicious.

